OL,3,CAnger as Bristol Rovers refers to
OL,4,C'disabled' and 'normal' fans
OL,6,FIt said: "We have provided all
OL,7,Fdisabled fans... to get free cards for
OL,8,Fthem upon request.
OL,10,F"As for normal fans and older fans,
OL,11,Fthey can purchase the card for #15,
OL,12,Fwhich is the exact cost on the club.
OL,14,F"We are not making any money on it,
OL,15,Fjust covering the costs."
OL,17,FThe club has since issued a statement
OL,18,Fapologising for any offence called,
OL,19,Fsaying: "No harmful intention of
OL,20,Fmeaning was ever intended in the
OL,21,Fwording."
