OL,3,CAnger as Bristol Rovers refers to
OL,4,C'disabled' and 'normal' fans
OL,6,FBut fans were quick to label the
OL,7,Fwording "extremely insensitive" and
OL,8,FBristol Rovers Disabled Supporters'
OL,9,FAssociation (DSA) said it is
OL,10,F"disappointed" in the wording used.
OL,12,F"We are disappointed to see (the) word
OL,13,F'normal' used in this context," they
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,F"One area agreed with Club for 2024/25
OL,17,Fis a review of comms and styles to
OL,18,Freflect what is current best practice."
