OL,3,CAnger as Bristol Rovers refers to
OL,4,C'disabled' and 'normal' fans
OL,6,FIn a reply to another post, the DSA
OL,7,Fsaid: "We do get folk make slip-ups -
OL,8,Fwe are all human.
OL,10,F"It's a word our working group picked
OL,11,Fup more than once in historic
OL,12,Fdocuments on the website which we are
OL,13,Fworking together to review/replace
OL,14,Fthis summer as well as knowledge
OL,15,Frefreshers.
OL,17,F"We can only make it better together."
OL,19,FOne fan of the club, Jake Barber,
OL,20,Fexplained why the word had upset him
OL,21,Fso much.
