OL,4,C'disabled' and 'normal' fans
OL,6,FJake later posted a video message and
OL,7,Fsaid: "I don't think they meant any
OL,8,Fharm. I'd like to think they didn't
OL,9,Fmean any harm, but like I said just
OL,10,Fbecause you're not in a wheelchair,
OL,11,Fdoesn't mean that you don't need
OL,12,Faccess to disabled facilities or help
OL,13,Flike that.
OL,15,F"I just think the club have worded
OL,16,Fthat awfully, so do better," he added
