OL,3,CAnger as Bristol Rovers refers to
OL,4,C'disabled' and 'normal' fans
OL,6,F"Bristol Rovers Football Club would
OL,7,Flike to apologise for any offence
OL,8,Fcaused by an error in wording in a
OL,9,Frecent communication regarding
OL,10,Fdisabled supporters.
OL,12,F"No harmful intention of meaning was
OL,13,Fever intended in the wording, which
OL,14,Fwas included in a private email
OL,15,Fexchange between the Club and a
OL,16,Frepresentative from the Bristol Rovers
OL,17,FSupporters Club.
