OL,6,F"The Club is proud of our ongoing
OL,7,Fcommitment to provide the best
OL,8,Fexperience for all supporters of
OL,9,FBristol Rovers FC, in particular our
OL,10,Fwork with the Club's Disabled
OL,11,FSupporters Association to ensure fans
OL,12,Fwith accessibility or additional needs
OL,13,Fare able to enjoy each and every match
OL,14,Fat The Memorial Stadium.
OL,16,F"In addition, the Club were recently
OL,17,Fcommended by the EFL by achieving
OL,18,FBronze in the EFL Equality Code of
OL,19,FPractice.
